  "warnings": [
    "Bun is NOT a UA-supported resolver (js-bun is Bucket C in whitesource-config.md). No .whitesource file is emitted — manual tool version pinning via scanSettings.versioning is impossible for this ecosystem. Detection is lockfile-driven (bun.lock JSONC parsing). Reproducibility guarantee is reduced.",
    "OVERRIDE SIGNAL: qs natural version from express@4.21.2 is 6.13.0. The root package.json overrides block forces qs to 6.5.3. The lockfile records qs@6.5.3. A correct Mend scan MUST report qs@6.5.3. If Mend reports qs@6.13.0 instead, it ignored the overrides field — that is the bug this probe targets.",
    "qs appears as a child of both express and body-parser in the dep graph. Both edges resolve to the override-applied version (6.5.3). If Mend reports two different qs versions (one 6.13.0, one 6.5.3) or reports qs twice, that is a deduplication + override failure.",
    "Paired probes (Tier 3): bun-overrides-1.0-flat-probe (#11) and bun-overrides-1.1-scoped-probe (#12) will exercise the scoped override form ('express > qs': '6.5.3') across Bun version boundaries. This probe (Tier 1 #3) uses the simpler unscoped form."
  ]
